 618:src/main.cpp  ****     // Idle behaviour: sweep a virtual position 0ŌåÆ1000ŌåÆ0 through the same
 619:src/main.cpp  ****     // LED-tent math as the pitch mapping (LED2=pos 0, LED1=middle, LED3=pos 1),
